    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you reach 15th level, you can discorporate into your swarm, avoiding danger. When you take damage, you can use your reaction to give yourself <strong>resistance </strong>to that damage. You vanish into your swarm and then teleport to an unoccupied space that you can see within <strong>30 feet</strong> of you, where you reappear with the swarm.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
